long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Twitter lists data from the list search page to a Excel/CSV/JSON file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the Twitter List Search Page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then right-click anywhere on the page.
3️⃣ Select "Extract Twitter List Search" from the menu.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in twitter list search result page.
2️⃣ Running solely on your local machine.
3️⃣ Export twitter list data to a Excel/CSV/JSON file, include infos of list, author etc.

✨ Why use this:
👩‍🔬 Obtain data for research and social listening experiments
🦠 Analyze trends, viral campaigns and content of specific creators
🥸 Identify unverified content and inaccurate information with high public value
📚 Prepare for or analyze a Twitter marketing campaign

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Twitter❗️🔒
